<h2><span id="2._g3_-_King.27s_Indian_Attack"></span><span id="2._g3_-_King's_Indian_Attack">2. g3 - King's Indian Attack</span></h2>
<p>White is most likely aiming to establish a King's Indian Attack. The idea is very similar to that of the King's Indian Defence as played by Black. The extra tempo enables White to take a more aggressive approach to the system.
</p>
